  "texts": [
    "The computing power required for the DTN may be distributed in different network nodes.",
    "A DTN element may colocate with the actual network element or be instantiated in a cloud platform.",
    "If a network node is prepared to support a digital twin service, it should report its capability to the cloud platform or the digital twin service controller for registration.",
    "In case of changes in the capability, the network node should report its new ability to assist the orchestration in the controller.",
    "The digital twin service controller must instruct the cloud platform or the corresponding network nodes to initialize digital twin scenes."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}